quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  14,11,"Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen maakani …ďe: "[Ko goonga], min ngonaani si wanaa …ďanndiŇčkoo…ďe yeru mon, kono Alla no mo∆ī∆īoo e mo o muuyi e jeyaa…ďe makko …ďeen. Laatanaaki min nde min ngaddana on hujja, si wanaa e duŇčayee Alla. Ko e Alla gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen pawotoo."
  14,12,"Ko ha…óata men nde pawotoo e Alla, gooŇč…óii o fewnii min (e) laawi amen? Ma min mu√Ī√Īo e kon ko lorroton men. Ko e Alla gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen pawotoo"."
  14,13,"∆Āeen yeddu…ďe (kadi) mbi'ani nulaa…ďe mun …ďen: "Ma min njaltin on ka leydi amen, maa ndutto…óon e diina amen". Joomi ma…ď…ďe wahayini e ma…ď…ďe: "Ma min kalku too√Īu…ďe …ďeen,"
  14,14,"Ma lin ko…ónu on e leydi ndin …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe. ∆äuum ko wonan¬īde on kul…óo daroyagol yeeso Am, o huli kammbaa am on".(sapporam.)"
  14,15,"∆Āe …óa…ď…ďi uddita, sooyi kala dunndaranke ∆īaggu…óo."
  14,16,"Jahannama no yesso makko, himo yarniree ndiyam mbordi ∆īii∆īiiri,"
  14,17,"homo woo…ďa …óam, e …óe…ďataa …ďennugol …óam. maayde ndeen ardana mo e kala nokku, kono o wonaani maayoowo. Hara no yeeso makko lepte cattu…óe."
  14,18,"Ko woni sifa …ďeen yeddu…ďe Joomi mun, kuu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, ko wano ndoondi ndi henndu tii…ói e mun, e √Īalaande bippoore. ∆Āe hettoytaa huunde e ko …ďe paggitinoo. Ko …óuum woni majjere won…ó…óunde."